{"tid":1639081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"快啲入黎睇清楚 連登仔們可唔可以威返次","createTime":"2019-10-08T13:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T13:49:19.000Z","uid":151605,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2818d4a668f37a691e9232f8fb433289c14844a1","tid":1639081,"uid":151605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:40:04.000Z","msg":"咁多位lihkg 巴絲想講既係政府個垃圾蒙面法<br />\n唔係限制埋所有人係平日日常唔可以戴口罩架<br />\n今日係條街戴個口罩 一個二個當我異類咁 屌<br />\n爭氣返少少喇 而家貼埋出黎俾你地睇清楚<br />\n聽日一個二個好戴返住個口罩<br />\n<br />\n在什麼情況下蒙面會觸法？<br />\n1. 經警方批出不反對通知書的集會與遊行。<br />\n2. 未經批准的集結。<br />\n3. 非法集結與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n哪些人可豁免?<br />\n1. 從事專業或受僱工作，為其個人人身安全理由，要蒙面在集會遊行現場出現者，如執勤員警。<br />\n2. 因宗教信仰要遮掩面部者。<br />\n3. 因先前已存在的醫學或健康理由，而要戴口罩等人士。<br />\n<br />\n一旦違法，罰則為何?<br />\n違法者最高監禁一年、罰款 2.5萬港幣(折台幣約 9.85萬元)。<br />\n<br />\n警方可隨時在公共場合要求民眾拿下面罩嗎？<br />\n可以，拒絕拿下面罩者，最高監禁六個月、罰款 1萬港幣(折台幣約 3.94萬元)。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命 香港人 反抗</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e82eff6f657ba69a0f7e88cf05227675e409197","tid":1639081,"uid":151605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:43:58.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"a0dce01bf2f7dacbaeaa8fe19339943f41a7f875","tid":1639081,"uid":151605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:44:09.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"c789381d3f3167558e1daa9a03047fa80917dfa3","tid":1639081,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/